                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t17880227-40-victim436 t17880227-40-viclabel202"></join>; on the 20th instant about half past one in the day, the prisoner was brought to my house by a constable, with a half gallon pot of mine; I had the pot in my hand about half an hour before at the cellar head; I saw the prisoner in the house about that time.</p>
